</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
ATHENS 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Iran's paramilitary Revolutionary Guards will launch an operation in the 
southeast of the country next week against rebels and drug traffickers, Tehran 
Radio said Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
The announcement followed a report Tuesday that paramilitary guards clashed 
with a 12-man gang of drug traffickers in the southeastern Iranian desert, 
killing five and wounding seven. 
</P>
