</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
WELLS FARGO BANK; LIENS; APPEALS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA010490-0161 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 157471 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 4, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 2; Column 1; Financial Desk 
