<P>
Hat Pins -- A Dec. 22 story about antique hat pins incorrectly described the 
price range of the collectibles. According to Melinda Churchfield of My Mom and 
Me in Laguna Niguel, 8- to 12-inch hat pins sell for $20 and up, and hat-pin 
holders start at $50. 
