</DATE>
<P>
ERICH LEINSDORF 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 1; Column 6; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
1015 words 
</P>
