parks. The 29-year-old "born again" Christian has been accused of blurring the 
line between religion and politics. But Parton and supporters say it's simply a 
misunderstanding. JUANITO HOLANDEZ / For The Times; Photo, Brad Parton has 
managed to stir things up in Redondo Beach after just eight months as mayor. ED 
